42:15.700 --> 42:17.200
But I do.

42:20.600 --> 42:24.800
Michael has tried to get through to you all evening
to no avail.

42:24.900 --> 42:26.500
That's not true.

42:26.700 --> 42:28.700
I smile and smile and smile...

42:28.750 --> 42:31.200
You're lying to all of us.

