44:04.361 --> 44:05.361
Mom...

44:08.100 --> 44:10.200
I'm a bit scared.

44:12.200 --> 44:13.700
A bit?

44:15.700 --> 44:18.700
I'd be scared out of my wits if I were you.

44:19.000 --> 44:22.200
No, it's something else, I...

44:24.700 --> 44:26.900
I'm frightened, Mom.

